# =============================================================================
# PRODUCTION SAFETY NOTES
# =============================================================================
# 
# ⚠️  CRITICAL: These files are excluded to protect production:
# 
# - All .db/.sqlite files (including live production database)
# - All .env files (containing API keys and secrets)  
# - Session files (user session data)
# - Backup files (could contain sensitive data)
# - IDE files (personal development settings)
# - Temporary files (could contain sensitive runtime data)
# 
# ✅ Only these files should reach production:
# - Source code (.js, .html, .css)
# - Configuration templates (not actual config)
# - Documentation (.md files)
# - Package.json (dependencies)
# 
# =============================================================================
